description: Crock Spot offers classic american cuisine, with an international twist. All of our meats are slow roasted to perfection in good ole fashioned crock pots; served over grain varietal and topped with a sauces of choice. Currently Crock Spot is a mobile food kitchen serving Denver's local festivals, markets and events. You will soon see Crock Spot rolling around in a mobile food truck and in the coming months a brick and mortar. Stay tuned! Crock Spot is a great option for your next catered event or party.
name: Crock Spot
